              Stage 2B: Dynamic Championship Re-Prediction
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                             │
│             Updated Feature Dataset                                         │
│                         │                                                   │
│                         ▼                                                   │
│             Reuse Stage 1 Prediction Pipeline                               │
│                         │                                                   │
│                         ▼                                                   │
│             Re-run Trained ML Model                                         │
│             No retraining during tournament                                 │
│                         │                                                   │
│                         ▼                                                   │
│             Model Probability                                               │
│             Latest ML probability based on current features                 │
│                         │                                                   │
│                         ▼                                                   │
│             Apply Live Tournament Rules                                     │
│                                                                             │
│             • Eliminated teams receive 0 probability                        │
│             • Remaining teams are renormalized                              │
│             • Active / Eliminated status is tracked                         │
│                                                                             │
│                         │                                                   │
│                         ▼                                                   │
│             Live Champion Probabilities                                     │
│                         │                                                   │
